House Resolution 163
By: Representatives Gaines of the 120th, Wiedower of the 121st, and Frye of the 122nd
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the North Oconee High School football team for winning the 2024 GHSA
2 Class 4A State Football Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the North Oconee High School football team has established and maintained
4 a proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, this superlative team has completed another triumphant season of football
6 competition by posting an undefeated record of 15 wins; and
7 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
8 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
9 2024 campaign, the team captured the first state championship in program history; and
10 WHEREAS, the team brought special recognition to its school and to Oconee County by
11 winning the 2024 GHSA Class 4A State Football Championship against Marist with a final
12 score of 14-7; and
13 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
14 athletic ability, dedication, hard work, and unity of purpose and spirit of each member of the
